Virgo is not your average bot. Her past was intense and weird. After ariving
on earth in a stasis pod, with the name of Stingtra, she met 2 Predacons,
Mantella and Drazom. Her first fight was on the side of Mantella and Drazom,
fighting Wrath and Kamodia. The 3 Preds claimed victory over the 2 Maxis,
and Mantella and Drazom took her to the Pred base. Soon she was a new member
of the Predacons. She soon set her sights on a bot named Quickstrike,
developing a crush on him. She behaved weirdly, such as making attempts to
protect him, and even cooked for him once. She slowly started getting the
idea that she did not appeal to Quickstrike. She even began torturing
herself. Nothing changed except Mantella and Drazom were gone. Mantella left
for another team, and Drazom was dead. She changed her name to Solo, seeing
how it fit better. She started torturing herself more and more. When she had
enough of the pain, she had planned to commit suicide, throwing herself of a
mountain. But instead of dying, she struck her head, losing her memory. She
was found by a Pred named Wildfire, and taken back to the Pred base. She
started going on a rampage, hitting the walls, throwing things, and
torturing herself worse then ever. She was told by Wildfire, that this was
home. She started running around the base, till banging her head and losing
her memory again. Confused, she left the base and wondered around, till
finding a base. When asked her name, she looked at what she charved on her
arm before she lost her memory the second time. She had charved the word
&quot;Virgo&quot; on her arm. Now settled in her new home, she still acts weirdly and
still finds the time for mutalation, but she hasn&#39;&#39;t lost her memory
since...

